<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>수정하기::<%= postsDetail.title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/upload.css">
</head>
<body>
    <img id="imgLogo" onclick="location.href='/api/main'" style="cursor:pointer;" src="https://github.com/eunji624/node-teamProject-newsFeed/blob/dev/public/images/logo_img.png?raw=true" >
    <div class="postingForm">
        <form class = "postingFormtag" method="POST" id="postEditForm" action='/api/post/modify/<%= postsDetail.id %>?_method=patch' >
            <h4>수정하기::<%= postsDetail.title %></h4>
            <p>제목 <input class = "postingInput" type="text"  placeholder="제목를 입력해 주세요" name="title" value="<%= postsDetail.title %>"> </p>
            <p>동물이름<input class = "postingInput" type="text"  placeholder="동물이름을 입력해 주세요" name="petName" value="<%= postsDetail.petName %>"></p> 
            <p>카테고리 <select name="category" class="form-select form-select-lg mb-3" id="floatingSelect" aria-label="Floating label select example">
                <option selected disabled ><%= postsDetail.category %></option>
                <option value="cat">cat</option>
                <option value="dog">dog</option>
                <option value="bird">bird</option>
                <option value="reptiles">reptiles</option>
            </select></p>
            <p>게시글 내용<input class = "postingInput" type="text"  placeholder="내용을 입력해 주세요" name="content" value="<%= postsDetail.content %>"></p>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary" id="postEditCorrectBtn">확인</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>